{"tha-ap5:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap5:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap5:0.3":"Mahakassapattheraapadana ","tha-ap5:1.1":"â€œPadumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap5:1.2":"Lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap5:1.3":"Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap5:1.4":"Pujam kubbanti satthuno. ","tha-ap5:2.1":"Udaggacitta janata, ","tha-ap5:2.2":"amoditapamodita; ","tha-ap5:2.3":"Tesu samvegajatesu, ","tha-ap5:2.4":"piti me udapajjatha. ","tha-ap5:3.1":"Natimitte samanetva, ","tha-ap5:3.2":"idam vacanamabravim; ","tha-ap5:3.3":"Parinibbuto mahaviro, ","tha-ap5:3.4":"handa pujam karomase. ","tha-ap5:4.1":"Sadhuti te patissutva, ","tha-ap5:4.2":"bhiyyo hasam janimsu me; ","tha-ap5:4.3":"Buddhasmim lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap5:4.4":"kahama punnasancayam. ","tha-ap5:5.1":"Agghiyam sukatam katva, ","tha-ap5:5.2":"satahatthasamuggatam; ","tha-ap5:5.3":"Diyaddhahatthapatthatam, ","tha-ap5:5.4":"vimanam nabhamuggatam. ","tha-ap5:6.1":"Katvana hammiyam tattha, ","tha-ap5:6.2":"talapantihi cittitam; ","tha-ap5:6.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap5:6.4":"cetiyam pujayuttamam. ","tha-ap5:7.1":"Aggikkhandhova jalito, ","tha-ap5:7.2":"kimsuko iva phullito; ","tha-ap5:7.3":"Indalatthiva akase, ","tha-ap5:7.4":"obhasati catuddisa. ","tha-ap5:8.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap5:8.2":"katvana kusalam bahum; ","tha-ap5:8.3":"Pubbakammam saritvana, ","tha-ap5:8.4":"tidasam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap5:9.1":"Sahassayuttam hayavahim, ","tha-ap5:9.2":"Dibbayanamadhitthito; ","tha-ap5:9.3":"Ubbiddham bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap5:9.4":"Sattabhumam samuggatam. ","tha-ap5:10.1":"Kutagarasahassani, ","tha-ap5:10.2":"sabbasonnamaya ahum; ","tha-ap5:10.3":"Jalanti sakatejena, ","tha-ap5:10.4":"disa sabba pabhasayam. ","tha-ap5:11.1":"Santi annepi niyyuha, ","tha-ap5:11.2":"lohitangamaya tada; ","tha-ap5:11.3":"Tepi jotanti abhaya, ","tha-ap5:11.4":"samanta caturo disa. ","tha-ap5:12.1":"Punnakammabhinibbatta, ","tha-ap5:12.2":"kutagara sunimmita; ","tha-ap5:12.3":"Manimayapi jotanti, ","tha-ap5:12.4":"disa dasa samantato. ","tha-ap5:13.1":"Tesam ujjotamananam, ","tha-ap5:13.2":"obhaso vipulo ahu; ","tha-ap5:13.3":"Sabbe deve abhibhomi, ","tha-ap5:13.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap5:14.1":"Satthikappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap5:14.2":"ubbiddho nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap5:14.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap5:14.4":"pathavim avasim aham. ","tha-ap5:15.1":"Tatheva bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap5:15.2":"timsakkhattum ahosaham; ","tha-ap5:15.3":"Sakakammabhiraddhomhi, ","tha-ap5:15.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap5:16.1":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap5:16.2":"catudipamhi issaro; ","tha-ap5:16.3":"Tatthapi bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap5:16.4":"indalatthiva uggatam. ","tha-ap5:17.1":"Ayamato catubbisam, ","tha-ap5:17.2":"vittharena ca dvadasa; ","tha-ap5:17.3":"Rammanam nama nagaram, ","tha-ap5:17.4":"dalhapakaratoranam. ","tha-ap5:18.1":"Ayamato pancasatam, ","tha-ap5:18.2":"vittharena tadaddhakam; ","tha-ap5:18.3":"Akinnam janakayehi, ","tha-ap5:18.4":"tidasanam puram viya. ","tha-ap5:19.1":"Yatha sucighare suci, ","tha-ap5:19.2":"pakkhitta pannavisati; ","tha-ap5:19.3":"Annamannam paghattenti, ","tha-ap5:19.4":"akinnam hoti lankatam. ","tha-ap5:20.1":"Evampi nagaram mayham, ","tha-ap5:20.2":"hatthissarathasankulam; ","tha-ap5:20.3":"Manussehi sadakinnam, ","tha-ap5:20.4":"rammanam nagaruttamam. ","tha-ap5:21.1":"Tattha bhutva pivitva ca, ","tha-ap5:21.2":"puna devattanam gato; ","tha-ap5:21.3":"Bhave pacchimake mayham, ","tha-ap5:21.4":"ahosi kulasampada. ","tha-ap5:22.1":"Brahmannakulasambhuto, ","tha-ap5:22.2":"maharatanasancayo; ","tha-ap5:22.3":"Asitikotiyo hitva, ","tha-ap5:22.4":"hirannassapi pabbajim. ","tha-ap5:23.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap5:23.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap5:23.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap5:23.4":"katam buddhassa sasanamâ€. ","tha-ap5:24.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahakassapo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap5:25.1":"Mahakassapattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}